name: Stuck
description:
I have decided to split these LoRAs into separate entities here on CivitAI, in order to keep it clean and enable versioning. Therefore, check the search box for any "Stuck in"/"Stuck on" LoRAs.

Currently, I am re-training the stuck in washing machine locon with fewer keywords and more steps (6300) as it was too simplistic in the face area etc, I have removed most identifying features.

This place will host various LoRAs for generating "stuck chick".
Use the CivitAI version buttons over the images above to select which model you want. Only the latest of each is available, but I will try to remark in each "about this version" text or in the general descriptions below what has changed in the latest release(s).

  1. "Stuck in dog door" supports women stuck seen from the front and the rear, as well as from outside and inside.

    It should support sexual interaction but it may require lots of trial and error.
    It has issues, sometimes it will just stick the woman in a door opening and sometimes there's a window over the dog door instead of a wall or a door. It still often works regardless, exclaiming that this woman is indeed "stuck".

  2. "Stuck in washing machine" is a locon LoRA which supports women stuck either with their head or ass inside a washing machine, completely inside it, or halfway in.
    This is also a complex lora (actually it is a locon) and I will have to improve on it as soon as possible. It was trained with a dimension of around 200. I am having issues with faces seen outside when they are near the washing machine (I would like feedbacks from you when using various models)

    You have to load this LoRA as a lyco with the lycoris extension in a1111 (which is now included as a built-in extension). Instead of <lora:stuck-in-washing-machine:1> use <lyco:stuck-in-washing-machine:1> to activate it.

    Using the additional networks extension you will also be able to see which tags a LoRA is trained with, so you can use that for inspiration. I will upload tag lists as soon as i can.

The next LoRAs will feature women stuck in a car window, window (house), door, ladder, sofa, bed, wall, and under a bed.
